{
  "stem": "5430.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we managed-- he got a smuggler to take us across the border.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And so we packed up our things, whatever we had-- Oh, my sister gave birth to my nephew in Lodz, and he was an infant.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we went to smuggle across the border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And as soon as we got across, we got arrested by the German police, put in a prison camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they stripped everything that we had and whatever valuables we still had and sent us back to Poland and-- and to near [INAUDIBLE], there was a small town, Walbrzych.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "W-A-L-B-R-Z-Y-C-H.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Walbrzych, Near Breslau or [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And so at that point, I said, we're not going to stay here either.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I joined the-- a group of kids that were going to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The Aliyah Bet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't know if you've heard of the Aliyah Bet, the illegal immigration to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was a general-- I guess they-- they had some people from [?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Haganad ?] that came down to transport mainly youth and younger kids also.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so we went on this trip.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we got through from Poland, through Czechoslovakia, and we stopped in Bratislava.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Somehow they had it prearranged that we were Greeks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So they said don't speak any German.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Speak Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We didn't know Hebrew so-- no.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He says speak Greek.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So we used Hebrew words, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we got as far as Vienna-- in Vienna, Austria.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were joined by another group over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then we continued on to Salzburg, Austria, which is near the border of Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And at that time, I knew that my brother was in Munich or near Munich-- [INAUDIBLE]-- and I decided to join him.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know why.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
